    "offices_or_providers": ["Mid-Minnesota Legal Aid (e.g., Minneapolis: 111 N 5th St, Ste 100; serves Anoka, Hennepin counties and central MN)", "Central Minnesota Legal Services (21 counties)", "Justice North (northern MN)", "Minnesota Regional Legal Services (other areas)"]
